                <p><span v-text="$t('metrics.jvm.memory.heap')">Heap Memory</span> ({{formatNumber1(metrics.gauges['jvm.memory.heap.used'].value / 1048576)}}M / {{formatNumber1(metrics.gauges['jvm.memory.heap.max'].value / 1048576)}}M)</p>
